  "title": "Permanent IT Sales Executive (IoT / Smart Home / Technology) – Pre-Sales at Tampines, Up to $2,900 + Commission",
  "description": "<p><strong>- Permanent</strong></p><p><strong>- Up to $2,900 + Commission</strong></p><p><strong>- Standard work days, flexibility for weekends/PH (time off-in-lieu provided)</strong></p><p><strong>- Tampines</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Meet with homeowners, interior designers, and electricians to understand renovation and smart home needs.</li><li>Propose tailored smart home solutions that align with client requirements and lifestyle.</li><li>Explain IoT technologies and solutions in simple, client-friendly terms.</li><li>Answer client questions and provide technical clarifications during the pre-sales process.</li><li>Prepare and present quotations, proposals, and demonstrations.</li><li>Coordinate with project teams to ensure smooth installation and setup during renovations.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Period:</strong></p><ul><li>Permanent</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Location:</strong></p><ul><li>Tampines</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Working hours:</strong></p><ul><li>Standard workdays, with flexibility for weekends/public holidays to match renovation schedules or client handovers.</li><li>Time off-in-lieu will be provided where appropriate.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Salary:</strong></p><ul><li>Up to $2,900 + Commission</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Polytechnic Diploma in Information Systems, Infocomm Technology, or related field.</li><li>Minimum 1 year of experience (including internships/projects).</li><li>Strong communication and presentation skills; able to build rapport with both clients and partners (IDs, electricians, contractors).</li><li>Basic knowledge of networking and IoT (Wi-Fi, Zigbee, RF, IR, Bluetooth).</li><li>Interest in smart home technologies and eagerness to learn on the job.</li><li>Good organisational skills to handle multiple client projects.</li><li>Sales-driven mindset with willingness to hit monthly targets.</li></ul><p><strong>Nice-to-Have:</strong></p><ul><li>Familiarity with smart devices like Philips Hue, TP-Link, Sonos, or Google Home.</li><li>Pre-sales or customer-facing experience.</li><li>Basic scripting/automation knowledge (Python, Node-RED, Home Assistant).</li><li>Driver’s License (preferred) — as site visits to clients and renovation sites are required.</li><li>Ensure sales targets are met while maintaining strong client relationships.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly email your detailed resume (<strong>MS Word</strong> format is preferred):</p><p><strong>zikry@successhrc.com.sg </strong>(Reg No: <strong>R2198989</strong>)</p><p>Please ensure that applications sent through email are <strong>no bigger than 1Mb</strong>.</p><p>We thank all applicants for your interest but regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Success Resource Centre Pte Ltd</strong> (EA License Number: <strong>04C3201</strong>)</p><p>160 Robinson Road, #13-07/08/09 SBF Center, Singapore 068914</p><p>T: 6337 3183 | W: <a href=\"http://www.successhrc.com.sg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.successhrc.com.sg</a></p>",
